dct_description_sm: Compiled and Drawn in the Department of State, Division of Geography and Cartography, Feb. 28, 1944.
Shows various boundaries, railroads (including under construction), roads, airfields, oilfields, deserts, disputed territories, waterways, mountain ranges.
